        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "They stand there on the level sand, serene, bulky and immaculate.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "Thousands of birds appear in one view-a very remarkable sight.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "At first guano and eggs were collected.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "A tramway was laid down and small box cars were introduced, in which the collected material was piled and pushed down to the packing place.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "For several years this went on, and the birds themselves were not molested.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "At last, however, a tentacle of the feather trade octopus reached out to Laysan.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "Schlemmer the Slaughterer bought a cheap vessel, hired twenty three phlegmatic and cold blooded Japanese laborers, and organized a raid on Laysan.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "With the utmost secrecy he sailed from Honolulu, landed his bird killers upon the sea bird wonderland, and turned them loose upon the birds.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "For several months they slaughtered diligently and without mercy. Apparently it was the ambition of Schlemmer to kill every bird on the island.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "Three hundred thousand albatrosses, gulls, terns and other birds were butchered to make a Schlemmer holiday!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "Homer r Dill.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000014_000003",
