        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "Department of Agriculture) is consumedly interesting to the friends of birds.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "Here is what he has said regarding the evidences of bird slaughter:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "\"Our first impression of Laysan was that the poachers had stripped the place of bird life.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "An area of over three hundred acres on each side of the buildings was apparently abandoned.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000015_000004",
