        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "By Homer r Dill, page twelve.)",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "The report of Professor Bryan contains the following pertinent paragraphs:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "\"This wholesale killing has had an appalling effect on the colony....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000022_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000022_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "The colonies that remain are in a sadly decimated condition.... Over a large part of the island, in some sections a hundred acres in a place, that ten years ago were thickly inhabited by albatrosses not a single bird remains, while heaps of the slain lie as mute testimony of the awful slaughter of these beautiful, harmless, and without doubt beneficial inhabitants of the high seas.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "\"While the main activity of the plume hunters was directed against the albatrosses, they were by no means averse to killing anything in the bird line that came in their way....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "Fortunately, serious as were the depredations of the poachers, their operations were interrupted before any of the species had been completely exterminated.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1648_144971_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1648/144971/1648_144971_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "But the work of the Evil Genius of Laysan did not stop with the slaughter of three hundred thousand birds.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
