        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1648",
        "content": "mr Schlemmer introduced rabbits and guinea pigs; and these rapidly multiplying rodents now are threatening to consume every plant on the island.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
